Look at that guy in the back!
I think we are turning into a tourist attraction.
I have been so busy lately that finally being able to catch up is a bit of a relief.
High students are currently taking final exams.
I hate exams almost as much as I hate shiitake mushrooms.
I told you to not put any in my lunch.
Why did you put them in?
You are still an immature deity, and this only seems to prove my point.
If your brain cannot keep up with the schoolwork, then you might as well stop coming.
I am fine with Tomoe coming to school with me to watch over me, but...
What were you so busy with anyway?
You were not doing your job as a deity.
There is not much I can even do as deity.
You do not seem to know when to stop when it comes to girls either.
Keep sticking to Nanami like a piece of gum on her shoe, and she will start to to hate you.
Those words were so harsh that I get the feeling you do not like me.
Did not you say that you would rip my heart out?
But I never said anything about Nanami.
At least try to get along.
I still have not had a chance to thank Kurama-kun for saving me.
He is always surrounded by girls, so it is hard to approach him.
I finally convinced myself today to thank him.
How about I get him to talk to you, then?
I will make sure you get to talk to him in private.
I have always wanted to ask, but are you like a deity or something?
Yeah, you were warding off spirits the other day, for example.
I have not told anyone, I swear!
Over what Tomoe did after falling sick a few days ago...
I guess I am more of a person who answers prayers.
I have finally found what I can do.
Wow, it is too bad I have already decided not to accept these kinds of things.
I would be happy if you just bought my CD.
Hey, do not you think our exam is covering too much material?
Is not it on the same day as our English exam?
We should probably start studying soon.
It feels like my very existence suddenly vanished into thin air.
Could you keep that on for a bit?
I have a huge favor to ask you.
Could you wait in front of the chem lab?
A girl will come to you.
No one can see my hotness?
I am late because a teacher asked me to do something.
Um, thank you for helping me the other day.
I have not had the chance to thank you properly yet.
My heart skip a beat when I saw the bride...
Yo, get a load of her panties!
I am calling you Strawberry Panties from now on!
You are making quite the scene over one little peek up-skirt.
Seems like Nekota-san was able to thank him.
I am not too shabby when I try.
Does this count as tying their fates together?
Thinking that is all it takes is another one of your faults.
Do you think everything will work out with a girl as weak as her?
If she were to learn that she had her fate tied with a demon, she would not be thanking you anymore.
Maybe a human rejected him once!
Tomoe's not too optimistic, but I did the right thing, did not I?
It was for the best... probably.
I was just thinking about how it would be great if humans and demons could get along.
Come on, there has to be at least one human who you would like to be friends with.
You should give it a try!
As long as I can protect you, I will be content.
D-Do not act so casual about it.
I have a quick favor to ask.
I am Sakurada Yumi, a freshman.
I am in love with Tomoe-senpai!
Yet I have not had a single chance to talk to him!
I might never get a chance!
What is more is that you are always with him, Momozono-senpai!
To be frank, I wanted to know if you two were going out.
I-It is not like we are going out.
Could you please do me a favor, then?
You know how you always walk home with him?
Could you let me go with him today?
I do not need to use any special powers.
I will just tell him that I am going on ahead and leave without him.
Are you heading home alone today?
I wonder if Tomoe went home with her.
You should give it a try!
I should not have said that.
Could you let me go with him today?
I am the one who did this, but I still regret it.
If I would known that I would feel this bad, I would not have agreed.
I am in love with Tomoe-senpai!
What is the meaning of this?
Were you trying to hook me up with that human?
Did you think you were being considerate by getting us together?
Do not ever do something like that again.
Those words finally made me realize
I realized that I would fallen in love with him.
Why did you call me out here, Crow Goblin?
Oh, your little conversation just so happened to drift into my ears.
I figured I would give a certain fox a little advice.
For crying out loud, you are an absent-minded fox.
Nanami's going through something called puberty.
It is a time when most humans go through a bit of emotional upheaval.
You have no intention of being with a human, correct?
You should be more mindful of how you act around her.
The fact that she is your master can only complicate matters more.
Are you saying that my actions are confusing her?
Being a familiar must be hell.
Not to mention the fact that it is to a human, a human girl!
I told you that you should have taken me as your master.
Do not lump my master with ordinary girls...
who would let things like love get the better of them, Crow Goblin.
If I ever become a deity, I will order you to die.
Good to see you have big dreams.
Hey, want to get something to eat to celebrate the end of exams?
There is this really great donut shop!
At least I can get guys.
Momozono-san, you are not going out with Tomoe-kun?
Well, we are spend a lot of time together, but that is about it.
I guess we are kind of close...
He said I was important to him, but he never said anything about love.
We live together, but it is not like we have gone anywhere together.
If you are having trouble figuring out your relationship, try doing something new.
You have never gone on a date, right?
Try going somewhere you have not been to before and dress up really cute.
If guys think you are cute, they will naturally come to you.
Momozono-san, are you in love with Tomoe-kun?!
Ami, I think you are a few pages behind.
Tomoe always wants to rush home.
He always says that he has work to do around the shrine.
It is only a bit past noon.
I am going to try something new!
I do not think I have been to one since that elementary school field trip!
This aquarium has a dolphin splash show!
What is with you all of a sudden?
We are done with exams so I am just having some fun!
We came all the way here, so let us make the best of it!
Marine animals can be pretty big!
At least look at the fish!
Crap, he is not enjoying this at all.
Now it looks like I am just dragging him along.
I wonder what that line is!
Apparently they are doing a seal show!
A lot of your friends came to watch!
A round of applause for him!
If guys think you are cute, they will naturally come to you.
We got to see all the fishies, and Nanami is thrilled to have come here.
We came all the way out here.
We might as well get a look at the nighttime scenery.
I wish I would brought my camera!
I wonder if we can see our home.
There is something up with you.
I highly doubt you were just dying to see the fish or the nighttime scenery.
I want to ask one thing.
You are not falling in love with me, are you?
The Crow Goblin told me that girls in puberty fall for men easily.
If I do not watch what I do, then you might fall for me.
Then again, it was just that Crow Goblin running his mouth.
What if I said that I love you?
I will not fall in love with a human girl.
Let the breeze cool you down.
I will wait until you come to your senses.
Admit that you spoke on impulse, and I will let you down.
You said I was important to you!
Do not you love me back?
You never thought I was cute?
I cannot look Tomoe in the face anymore.
Using your words to force me...
You do not even like me!
I promise to never touch you again, but let me save you just this once!
You are so strong, warm, and kind, yet...
How can I just give up?
I am falling in love with you even more.
Such a courageous confession followed by immediate heartbreak!
The gang decides to take a trip to the beach only to be approached by
a black shadow from the sea claiming to have some business with Tomoe.
Next time: The Deity Goes to the Beach!
